@RobinMalfait 
I've found why  max-* fails.  
overrides default only cause the missing key fails, like missing `'sm'` only make `'max-sm'` fails
it is by extending with `raw`, make all the max-* fails

```
module.exports = {
  theme: {
    extend: {
      screens: {
        tall: { raw: '(min-height: 800px)' },
        laptop: '1024px',
      },
    },
  },
  plugins: [],
}
```

